cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is about multi-agent reinforcement learning with limited communication bandwidth and scheduling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers topics related to reinforcement learning. The paper also deals with multi-agent systems, which suggests cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) as the second likely category. The limited communication bandwidth and scheduling aspects of the paper suggest cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as a possible category. The paper also involves decision-making and optimization, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with coordination among agents, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
